      "short": "Helmholtz bowed string with H2 correction, Stradivari body EQ, and sympathetic resonance.",
      "long": "Full physical modelling of a bowed violin string using Helmholtz motion synthesis, H2 correction oscillator, inharmonicity chorus, 8-band Stradivari body resonances, sympathetic open-string resonance, and continuous pitch glide on the fingerboard. All parameters derived from peer-reviewed acoustic measurements (Schelleng 1973, Jansson 2002, Woodhouse 2004, Smith 2010)."
    }
